cxro.common.io.modbus.client

Class ReadRORegistersTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • cxro.common.io.modbus.client.ModbusTransaction
      • cxro.common.io.modbus.client.ReadRORegistersTransaction

  • public final class ReadRORegistersTransaction
extends ModbusTransaction
    Class implementing a ReadRORegisters transaction. The implementation directly correlates with the modbus function READ_INPUT_REGISTERS (FC 4). It encapsulates the corresponding request and response messages.

    RegistersRW are understood as 16-bit integers that can be manipulated (i.e. set or unset).
